title: Rehab: Party at the Hard Rock Hotel
overview: Rehab: Party at the Hard Rock Hotel follows the fun and action poolside, as seen from the perspectives of a tough-as-nails staff. The Rehab crew is led by general manager Justin, from New York; security veteran Sharon and her staffer "Deebo"; two sultry bartenders, Chantell and Christina; and two gorgeous cocktail waitresses, Kelly and Julia. Viewers will get an All-Access Pass as nearly inconceivable party stories unfold.
